Card: M10.5-3 — fix 4 P0 runtime bugs + S-3 finality logic
Date: 2026-05-24
Status: ☑

=== Fixes Applied ===

(a) chmigrate/011_buffer_account_id.sql: add account_id to md_ticks_buffer and md_bars_buffer.
(b) quality.Check(ctx, t): added context.Context parameter, updated all 3 callers
    (manager.HandleTick, e2e-check, quality internal DLQ calls).
(c) manager.HandleTick: 6-stage OTel span chain (normalize→quality→dedup→aggregate→publish→enqueue)
    via SimpleSpan no-op when tracer disabled.
(d) bar_aggregator.IngestExternalBar: changed from MAX-based comparison to exact-match dedup
    using map[finalizedKey]map[int64]struct{}. Historical backfill bars are no longer rejected.
    runner.go loadFinalizedBars: fatal-on-error (CH unreachable = refuse to start).
    Query uses FINAL to avoid duplicates.

